# ============================================================
#  JIRAIYA Dashboard — Repository Registry (TEMPLATE)
# ============================================================
#  Copy this file to ".env" and edit the paths for THIS machine:
#       cp .env.example .env
#
#  The dashboard's "// REPOSITORIES" panel is built from the lines below.
#  PHP reads .env server-side (never served over HTTP), so editing it is all
#  you need — no code changes. .env is git-ignored; this template is tracked.
#
#  Format, one repo per line:
#     REPO[]=Name | langs | note | path | active
#
#     • Name   — display name
#     • langs  — comma-separated tags: laravel, vue, angular, php, ts, md, js
#     • note   — short description shown under the name
#     • path   — absolute path to the repo on THIS machine
#     • active — optional 5th field; write "active" on exactly one repo to
#                highlight it as the current working repo
# ============================================================

REPO[]=Jiraiya       | php           | AI Memory Core  | /Applications/Sites/jiraiya          | active
REPO[]=Nilam         | laravel       | Laravel         | /Applications/Sites/nilam
REPO[]=MyStudent     | vue           | Vue SPA         | /Applications/Sites/mystudentvue
REPO[]=MyAlumniCard  | angular       | Angular         | /Applications/Sites/myalumni-angular
REPO[]=Masmed2u      | laravel       | API Backend     | /Applications/Sites/apps-back-end
REPO[]=Mobiliti UG   | laravel       | Laravel         | /Applications/Sites/mobilitiug
REPO[]=Credit        | laravel,vue   | Laravel + Vite  | /Applications/Sites/credit
REPO[]=Frontend Aduan| laravel       | Laravel         | /Applications/Sites/frontend-aduan
REPO[]=My HEP        | laravel,vue   | Laravel + Vite  | /Applications/Sites/hepweb
REPO[]=iCan2u        | laravel       | Laravel         | /Applications/Sites/ican2u
REPO[]=Lara1         | laravel       | Laravel         | /Applications/Sites/lara1
REPO[]=Result EJPP   | vue           | Vue SPA         | /Applications/Sites/result-ejpp
REPO[]=Weightloss    | vue           | Vue SPA         | /Applications/Sites/weightloss
